        "@language": "en-us",
        "@value": "Music Honours Performance Is the best of the best in Music.  Features Provincial Delegates as soloists and other award winners as soloists, duos, choirs and bands in all Specialties in Music; Piano, Strings, Classical Voice, Musical Theatre, Woodwinds, etc.Please come and support all these hard working young musicians, from 6 to 28, as they strive for perfection in their chosen craft."
      }
